swapCollected(string,string,uint256).details: The calling address must approve this contract to spend at least `amountIn` worth of its DAI for this function to succeed.
swapCollected(string,string,uint256).notice: swapExactInputSingle swaps a fixed amount of DAI for a maximum possible amount of WETH9 using the DAI/WETH9 0.3% pool by calling `exactInputSingle` in the swap router.

params.amountIn: The exact amount of DAI that will be swapped for WETH9.
